00:39:33.690 --> 00:39:37.110 align:middle line:84%
when I sometimes
pray for animals.

00:39:37.110 --> 00:39:42.710 align:middle line:84%
Recently coyotes had begun
to come outside my window

00:39:42.710 --> 00:39:43.640 align:middle line:90%
when I'm doing this.

00:39:43.640 --> 00:39:46.520 align:middle line:84%
And they look in and
fix me with their gaze

00:39:46.520 --> 00:39:50.120 align:middle line:84%
while I'm engaged in
meditation and prayer

00:39:50.120 --> 00:39:52.630 align:middle line:84%
for living things around
the house, my plants,

00:39:52.630 --> 00:39:55.050 align:middle line:84%
the birds at the feeders,
and all this kind of thing.

00:39:55.050 --> 00:39:57.051 align:middle line:84%
It's as if they
sense it and know it.

00:39:57.051 --> 00:39:58.550 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Now in the
studies that were

00:39:58.550 --> 00:40:02.190 align:middle line:84%
done-- that's a great thing
to try at home, by the way.

00:40:02.190 --> 00:40:04.190 align:middle line:84%
In the studies that were
done around the plants,

00:40:04.190 --> 00:40:06.064 align:middle line:84%
can you us a little
about the statistics that

00:40:06.064 --> 00:40:09.390 align:middle line:84%
were done with some growing more
than others, the prayed for,

00:40:09.390 --> 00:40:10.320 align:middle line:90%
not prayed for?

00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:12.910 align:middle line:84%
>>DOSSEY: Well, these
are very easy to do.

00:40:12.910 --> 00:40:17.690 align:middle line:84%
And just to speak generally,
the plants that are prayed for,

00:40:17.690 --> 00:40:20.260 align:middle line:84%
generally the seeds
germinate faster

00:40:20.260 --> 00:40:21.910 align:middle line:90%
than the un-prayed-for seeds.

00:40:21.910 --> 00:40:23.800 align:middle line:84%
The seedlings after
they germinate

00:40:23.800 --> 00:40:27.110 align:middle line:84%
grow faster than those
that are not prayed for.

00:40:27.110 --> 00:40:30.500 align:middle line:84%
I actually have
several children who

00:40:30.500 --> 00:40:34.320 align:middle line:84%
have done science projects
in the eighth grade who

00:40:34.320 --> 00:40:38.100 align:middle line:84%
have done these germination
experiments and the seedling

00:40:38.100 --> 00:40:39.270 align:middle line:90%
experiments.

00:40:39.270 --> 00:40:40.360 align:middle line:90%
It's interesting.

00:40:40.360 --> 00:40:43.100 align:middle line:84%
What these kids do is
to plant their seeds

00:40:43.100 --> 00:40:47.430 align:middle line:84%
and put a string down the middle
and just pray for the seeds

00:40:47.430 --> 00:40:49.560 align:middle line:84%
on this side of the string
and not the other ones.

00:40:49.560 --> 00:40:52.200 align:middle line:84%
And then they just
take serial pictures.

00:40:52.200 --> 00:40:54.140 align:middle line:90%
And they send me the pictures.

00:40:54.140 --> 00:40:57.560 align:middle line:84%
And almost invariably,
it's the prayed-for seeds

00:40:57.560 --> 00:40:59.960 align:middle line:90%
that germinate faster.

00:40:59.960 --> 00:41:04.550 align:middle line:84%
One little girl said that she
wasn't sure about this prayer

00:41:04.550 --> 00:41:08.700 align:middle line:84%
stuff, so in her experiment,
she recruited a nun

00:41:08.700 --> 00:41:10.536 align:middle line:90%
to pray along with her.

00:41:10.536 --> 00:41:12.690 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: [LAUGHS] She
didn't want to do it.

00:41:12.690 --> 00:41:14.880 align:middle line:84%
>>DOSSEY: She wanted
to make that she got--

00:41:14.880 --> 00:41:15.300 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It was done right.

00:41:15.300 --> 00:41:17.400 align:middle line:84%
>>DOSSEY: She got plenty
of good, solid prayer

00:41:17.400 --> 00:41:19.664 align:middle line:90%
in her experiment.

00:41:19.664 --> 00:41:20.830 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's a great idea.

00:41:20.830 --> 00:41:22.460 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you don't have to
be in eighth grade science

00:41:22.460 --> 00:41:22.960 align:middle line:90%
to do that.

00:41:22.960 --> 00:41:24.440 align:middle line:84%
You can definitely
do that at home.

00:41:24.440 --> 00:41:25.398 align:middle line:90%
>>DOSSEY: That's right.

00:41:25.398 --> 00:41:26.897 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So take a
plant and put it

00:41:26.897 --> 00:41:28.730 align:middle line:84%
in your window and pray
for, and another one

00:41:28.730 --> 00:41:33.100 align:middle line:84%
and let the sun do its work,
