I'm personally blown away
by the statistics around it

00:41:37.690 --> 00:41:39.820 align:middle line:84%
and the science that
has been done around it.

00:41:39.820 --> 00:41:42.760 align:middle line:84%
And I think there's a lot
to be gained and to learn.

00:41:42.760 --> 00:41:44.260 align:middle line:84%
Thank you, though,
for sharing that,

00:41:44.260 --> 00:41:46.429 align:middle line:84%
because it's the science
that I'm looking for.

