00:42:55.580 --> 00:43:00.030 align:middle line:84%
around how prayer is
completely effective in healing

00:43:00.030 --> 00:43:04.300 align:middle line:84%
plants, animals, funguses,
people-- double blind,

00:43:04.300 --> 00:43:06.140 align:middle line:84%
randomized studies
that have been done,

00:43:06.140 --> 00:43:07.639 align:middle line:84%
clinical studies
that have been done

00:43:07.639 --> 00:43:08.910 align:middle line:90%
over the past several decades.

00:43:08.910 --> 00:43:10.290 align:middle line:84%
And you've really been
responsible in bringing

00:43:10.290 --> 00:43:11.020 align:middle line:90%
this about.

00:43:11.020 --> 00:43:14.070 align:middle line:84%
How about the idea
of remote healing?

00:43:14.070 --> 00:43:17.150 align:middle line:84%
Can that be used to help someone
if they're in the hospital

00:43:17.150 --> 00:43:20.500 align:middle line:84%
